Bush 's Democratic rivals lashed out at Bush 's Iraq policy . Some rivals said that the attack was the latest proof of the failure of Bush 's Iraq policy .
Senator Edwards from North Carolina told the Columbian Broadcasting Corporation : " Our current policy has failed . I don 't know why the government is not willing to change the way . "
