With the lapse of time , two completely different worlds have appeared in China . One is the highly prosperous urban area and the other is the poor and backward countryside .
Quoting an official comment from China , the enlarging gap between China 's urban and rural areas is " a problem during the course of development " and will only be settled by sustainable development .
